import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Text, Heading, Center, Divider} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Header = () => {
    const header_border = {
        borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
      };
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Box maxW="600px" maxH="52px" >
                <Center>  
                    <Stack direction="row" spacing="500px" >
                        <Box>
                            <Text fontSize="19px" fontWeight="800" color="#FFFFFF" mt="10px">Home</Text>
                        </Box>
                        <Box>
                            <Text  w="23px" h="23px"  bg="tomato" mt="15px">.</Text>
                        </Box>
                    </Stack>
                </Center>
                
            </Box>
            <Box maxW="1240px" style={header_border} bg="tomato"></Box>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}


export default Header
